name: Invoked Nemesis
text: "Aleister the Invoker" + 2 "Gradius" This card's ATK/DEF is equal to the number of cards in your GY and both players Banished Zones x 300. All monsters on the field and in the GY's are treated as LIGHT and DARK Attribute. This card cannot be used as Fusion Material. Cannot be destroyed card effects.
